"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-olympics-2024-asher-smith-neita-team-gb-relay-b1175152.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  Dina Asher-Smithbelieves she and her fellowTeam GBsprinters can make their mark and come away with a medal in the 4x100m relays at the2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After what has been a difficultOlympic Games, Asher-Smith returned to some of her best form in the final of the 200monly to be denied a bronze medal by just two hundredths of a secondon Tuesday night.\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asher-Smith had been told by her coach Edrick 'Flo' Floreal before the race, \\\"if you die you die, just get out and keep going\\\".\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That do-or-die attitude very nearly got her a medal after a 100m performance that was well off her best and left her and her coaching team scratching their heads.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, she plans to leave Paris with a piece of silverware.\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 913, \"end\": 918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.9494319662384105e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really excited for the relay,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's going to be a fun couple of days for us.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Women's sprinting is really incredible right now.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a great time to be a female sprinter.\\\"\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Americans look set to be the strongest quartet in the relays while the Jamaicans have been shorn of some of their best pace women through injury.\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4870172314559525e-19, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 1222, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0704102854560603e-14, \"text\": \"Jamaicans\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024 medal table and latest count today  Olympics 2024: Every Team GB medal winner at the Paris Games so far  Asher-Smith said she would reflect on her two individual races as a stepping stone following a first season training outside the UK in Texas with a new coach after splitting with lifetime coach John Blackie.\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6330926621900607, \"rank\": 0.5795476012578211, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1552, \"end\": 1557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\", \"score\": 0.9999923273270399, \"rank\": 4.225916608383107e-06, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\"}, {\"begin\": 1616, \"end\": 1623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blackie_and_Son\", \"score\": 0.9999999985739123, \"rank\": 1.4261020708351428e-09, \"text\": \"Blackie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blackie_and_Son\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blackie_and_Son\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For a first year with a new coach, I think this is a great platform to build from,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Overall, I am happy because I have known I have been in a great place for this whole season.\\\"\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Daryll Neitawas just a further hundredth of a second behind in the 200m in fifth following on from an impressive fourth in the 100m.\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1949, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Neita revealed she had had a last-minute pep talk from Keely Hodgkinson, complete with a gold medal around her neck, telling her, \\\"just leave nothing to chance, just give it your all\\\".\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 2135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2006, \"end\": 2022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"It's amazing when you have got team-mates who are so open to share because not everybody might be so open.\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Keely is so open and inspiring, it's a really good energy to be around.\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was so close and you just want one of those medals.\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am so proud of myself and I know my time is coming.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have to be a little bit more patient.\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am hungry, I fought it all the way to the line.\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately, I do not have the medal around my neck.\\\"\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asher-Smith and Neita, who have been rivals since they were young girls, will reunite to become the fulcrum of the British sprint relay team in Paris.\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2701, \"end\": 2708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.898032114057164, \"rank\": 0.07100099235170129, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2730, \"end\": 2735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.9494319662384105e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The heats are on Thursday morning with the final on Friday evening.\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2804, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tuesday night's 200m final was won by American Gabby Thomas in a time of 21.83sec.\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2844, \"end\": 2852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999829659386874, \"rank\": 1.5282451197298162e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2853, \"end\": 2865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.507455417567345e-12, \"text\": \"Gabby Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 3768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2950, \"end\": 2959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999828729235245, \"rank\